 {"text": "We are a Delaware corporation that operates as the parent company of our hard drive business, Western Digital", "bbox": [185.5, 1206.3, 1094.1, 1227.1]}, {"text": "Technologies, Inc., which was formed in 1970.", "bbox": [143.8, 1231.3, 526.3, 1252.2]}, {"text": "Our principal executive offices are located at 20511 Lake Forest Drive, Lake Forest, California 92630. Our telephone", "bbox": [185.5, 1280.0, 1094.3, 1300.8]}, {"text": "number is (949) 672-7000 and our web site is http://www.westerndigital.com. The information on our web site is not", "bbox": [143.8, 1304.9, 1094.2, 1325.8]}, {"text": "incorporated in this Annual Report on Form 10-K.", "bbox": [143.8, 1330.0, 563.2, 1350.8]}, {"text": "Western Digital, WD, the WD logo, WD Caviar, WD Raptor, WD VelociRaptor, WD Scorpio, WD Elements, My", "bbox": [185.5, 1378.7, 1094.2, 1399.5]}, {"text": "Passport, My Book, My DVR Expander and GreenPower are trademarks of Western Digital Technologies, Inc. and/or its", "bbox": [143.8, 1403.6, 1094.2, 1424.4]}, {"text": "affiliates. All other trademarks mentioned are the property of their respective owners.", "bbox": [143.8, 1428.6, 841.4, 1449.5]}, {"text": "2", "bbox": [613.8, 1478.6, 624.3, 1499.4]}]}